## Your Task

Write a **linking axiom** — a universal rule that connects the orphaned predicate(s) to
the connected predicate vocabulary, thereby bridging the proof chain.

**Guiding question:** What general semantic relationship exists between the orphaned
predicate(s) `{{ orphaned_preds | join(", ") }}` and the connected predicates
