- The axiom MUST be a **universally quantified rule** (ForAll/Exists form).
  Do NOT output a ground fact (e.g. `is_stock(ko)`) — ground facts replace individual
  premises rather than bridging the proof chain.
- Use **ONLY** identifiers (predicates, constants, sorts, bound variables) already declared
